### Token holen
POST http://localhost:8180/realms/todo/protocol/openid-connect/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type = password &
client_id = todo-dev &
username = demo &
password = demo &
scope = openid

> {%
    client.global.set("token", response.body.access_token);
%}

### Alle To-Do-Listen abrufen
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/lists
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Einzelne To-Do-Liste abrufen
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/lists/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Alle Tasks einer bestimmten Liste abrufen (Response ohne listId)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/lists/1/tasks
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Neue To-Do-Liste erstellen
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/lists
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Work-{{$timestamp}}",
  "description": "Liste fuer Tasks-{{$timestamp}}"
}

